TITLE: Multiple API Methods in One Action (YAML)
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to execute multiple API methods in a single action, including file creation and node restart.
SOURCE: https://github.com/virtuozzo/cloudscripting-docs/blob/master/docs/creating-manifest/actions.md#2025-04-23_snippet_19

LANGUAGE: yaml
CODE:
```
type: update
name: API action

onInstall:
  api:
    - method: environment.file.Create
      params:
        nodeGroup: cp
        path: /tmp/exampleFile.txt
    - method: environment.control.RestartNodes
      params:
        nodeGroup: cp
```

