TITLE: Configuring Conditional Filters for List Fields in Cloudscripting (YAML)
DESCRIPTION: This YAML snippet demonstrates how to set up conditional filters for list fields using the 'dependsOn' property. It shows a non-strict order example with two interconnected list fields.
SOURCE: https://github.com/virtuozzo/cloudscripting-docs/blob/master/docs/creating-manifest/visual-settings.md#2025-04-23_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: yaml
CODE:
```
type: install
name: Conditional filters for type "list"

settings:
  fields:
    - caption: List 1
      type: list
      name: list1
      default: value1
      required: true
      values:        
        value1: one
        value2: two
        value3: three

    - caption: List 2
      type: list
      name: list2
      required: true      
      dependsOn:                 
        list1:
            value1:              
              1: 1
              one: one
            value2:    
              2: 2
              two: two
            value3:               
              3: 3
              three: three
```

