TITLE: Configuring regionlist Field in Cloud Scripting Manifest
DESCRIPTION: Defines a regionlist field that allows users to select from available regions. Includes options for filtering regions by various criteria, handling inactive regions, and automatic selection of the first available region.
SOURCE: https://github.com/virtuozzo/cloudscripting-docs/blob/master/docs/creating-manifest/visual-settings.md#2025-04-23_snippet_28

