TITLE: Configuring Strict Order Conditional Filters for List Fields in Cloudscripting (YAML)
DESCRIPTION: This YAML snippet demonstrates how to set up strict order conditional filters for list fields using the 'dependsOn' property. It shows an example with two interconnected list fields and ordered options.
SOURCE: https://github.com/virtuozzo/cloudscripting-docs/blob/master/docs/creating-manifest/visual-settings.md#2025-04-23_snippet_9

LANGUAGE: yaml
CODE:
```
type: install
name: Conditional filters for type "list"

settings:
  fields:
    - caption: List 1
      type: list
      name: list1
      default: value1
      required: true
      values:        
        - value: value1
          caption: one
        - value: value2
          caption: two
        - value: value3
          caption: three

    - caption: List 2
      type: list
      name: list2
      required: true      
      dependsOn:                 
        list1:
            value1:
