SOURCE: https://github.com/virtuozzo/cloudscripting-docs/blob/master/docs/creating-manifest/actions.md#2025-04-23_snippet_55

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "update",
  "name": "Assert action - script action assert",
  "onInstall": [
    {
      "cmd [cp]": "echo test"
    },
    {
      "script": [
        "return {",
        "   result : 0,",
        "   test: '123'",
        "};"      ]
    },
    {
      "assert": [
