TITLE: Implementing UML Conversion Script in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This JavaScript script implements the conversion of UML diagrams. It targets elements with classes 'uml-flowchart' and 'uml-sequence-diagram', renders the UML content using the appropriate library, and replaces the original source with the rendered diagram.
SOURCE: https://github.com/virtuozzo/cloudscripting-docs/blob/master/3rdparty/pymdown-extensions/docs/src/markdown/extensions/superfences.md#2025-04-23_snippet_22

LANGUAGE: javascript
