TITLE: Configuring MathJax using JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This JavaScript snippet configures the MathJax library. It specifies the input (TeX) and output (HTML-CSS, NativeMML) formats, loads necessary extensions (tex2jax, MathMenu, MathZoom), defines delimiters for inline ('\\(','\\)') and display ('\\[','\\]') math, sets display alignment to left, and hides processing messages.
