TITLE: ShowIf with String Field
DESCRIPTION: Example of using showIf with a string field to display a custom string field when 'custom' is entered in both YAML and JSON formats.
SOURCE: https://github.com/virtuozzo/cloudscripting-docs/blob/master/docs/creating-manifest/visual-settings.md#2025-04-23_snippet_59

LANGUAGE: yaml
CODE:
```
type: install
name: ShowIf support with string field

settings:    
  fields:
    - type: string
      caption: String
      placeholder: type 'custom'
      showIf:
        custom:
          - type: string
            caption: Custom
```

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "install",
  "name": "ShowIf support with string field",
  "settings": {
    "fields": [
      {
        "type": "string",
        "caption": "String",
        "placeholder": "type 'custom'",
        "showIf": {
          "custom": [
            {
              "type": "string",
              "caption": "Custom"
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

