TITLE: Documenting onBeforeAttachExtIp Event in Markdown
DESCRIPTION: Describes the onBeforeAttachExtIp event triggered before attaching an external IP address. It details event placeholders for both params and response.
SOURCE: https://github.com/virtuozzo/cloudscripting-docs/blob/master/docs/creating-manifest/events.md#2025-04-23_snippet_11

LANGUAGE: markdown
CODE:
```
### onBeforeAttachExtIp

The event is executed before attaching the external IP address. The *onBeforeAttachExtIp* event is triggered each time before the external IP address attachment.

**Event Placeholders:**

- `${event.params.}`:
    - `nodeid` - node identifier for attaching external IP address
    - `session` - current user session
    - `envName` - environment unique appid
    - `appid` - application unique appid
    - `name` - environment display name
    - `env` - environment short domain name
- `${event.response.}`:
    - `result` - parameters are absent
```

