SOURCE: https://github.com/virtuozzo/cloudscripting-docs/blob/master/3rdparty/mkdocs/mkdocs/tests/integration/subpages/docs/sub1/sub1a/non-index.md#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: Markdown
CODE:
```
![Image](../image.png)
```

LANGUAGE: Markdown
CODE:
```
![Image](../../image.png)
```

